-------------------------------------
构建：
$ ros2 pkg create basic_ros2  --build-type ament_cmake --dependencies rclcpp --node-name demo
$ colcon build --packages-select basic_ros2
$ source install/setup.bash
$ ros2 run basic_ros2 demo 
  输出语句--- hello world basic_ros2 package


-------------------------------------
定义interface 流程：

step0:
功能包创建：
    ros2 pkg create --build-type ament_cmake base_interfaces_demo
    创建过程 没有添加任何依赖

step1:
package.xml
    <depend>geometry_msgs</depend>
    <buildtool_depend>rosidl_default_generators</buildtool_depend>
    <exec_depend>rosidl_default_runtime</exec_depend>
    <member_of_group>rosidl_interface_packages</member_of_group>

    通过指令查询：
        $ ros2 pkg list | grep -i rosidl

step2:
cmakelist.txt
    find_package(rosidl_default_generators REQUIRED)
    #为接口文件生成源代码
    rosidl_generate_interfaces{ ${PROJECT_NAME}
        "msg/Student.msg"
    }

step3:
编写msg:Student 
    名称:首字母必须大写
    数据类型：
        int8, int16, int32, int64 (或者无符号类型: uint*)
		float32, float64
		string
		time, duration
        
编译功能包：
    $ colcon build --packages-select base_interfaces_demo 
    $ source install/setup.bash

验证：
    查看该pkg下有哪些可用的interface
    $ ros2 interface package basic_interfaces_demo
    显示
    $ ros2 interface show basic_interfaces_demo/msg/Num


